          <li><strong>Frameworks:</strong> Ruby on Rails, React, Next.js, Node.js</li>
          <li><strong>Backend & Data Systems:</strong> PostgreSQL, MySQL, Redis, Apache Kafka, Sidekiq, GraphQL, REST APIs</li>
          <li><strong>Infrastructure & DevOps:</strong> AWS (S3, ECS), Docker, Heroku, CI/CD Pipelines</li>
          <li><strong>Quality & Observability:</strong> RSpec, TDD (Test-Driven Development), Datadog, Performance Profiling, Incident Response</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 id="beyond-the-code">Beyond the code</h2>
        <p>
          I'm a strong advocate for technical craftsmanship and engineering discipline. Over my 10+ years in the industry, I have active experience mentoring junior and mid-level developers in test-driven development (TDD) and clean code practices, helping teams increase test coverage (up to 95%) and significantly lower production defect rates.
        </p>
        <p>
          My background in ALT design and visual art keeps me connected to creative work outside of pure backend programming. I enjoy exploring layout aesthetics, human-computer interfaces, and experimenting with graphics tools.
